title: (Thurs Early Bird) Amy Checks in From Hollywood with Her No. 1 Highlight! + Would the Guys Have Surgery to Grow Taller? +  Elder vs. Millennial
itunes:title: (Thurs Early Bird) Amy Checks in From Hollywood with Her No. 1 Highlight! + Would the Guys Have Surgery to Grow Taller? +  Elder vs. Millennial
description:
Amy checks in from LA to share with us her number 1 highlight from being on set! There’s a story about a guy who is recovering from surgery to add 3 inches to his height. The guys debate if they would do this procedure. And Eddie and Morgan face off in this week’s round of generational trivia: Elder vs. Millennial.
